((* if c.e2e *))
\section{Real End-to-End Test (UERANSIM gNB + UE)}
\noindent The suites above drive the UPF's data plane directly. To validate the full chain,
a simulated 5G phone and radio (UERANSIM) was attached to the live core and real traffic was
pushed through this UPF --- the same path a production subscriber's data takes
(radio $\rightarrow$ N3 $\rightarrow$ UPF $\rightarrow$ N6 $\rightarrow$ internet).\\[4pt]
\noindent\textbf{Connectivity:} (((  c.e2e.ping | tex  ))).\\[6pt]
